{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-8", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "灰燼中的詩", "storyInfo": "深池“領袖”處決了洩露聚會訊息的女孩。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  領袖，人找到了。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好，帶上來吧。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  幹什麼！你、你放開我！", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是你把聚會的消息傳給維多利亞軍的？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  什麼？你怎麼知......", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  等一下，你、你是......你是那個人？！你就是總編他們說的人......", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  跟他們說的那樣，你會帶來一場戰爭，領著我們趕走壓迫者？", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不......你會帶來死亡......把我們的家園化作廢墟，就像現在這樣。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  一切的源頭，都是你！", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我將帶來的只有勝利。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而你，西爾莎·凱利，你深深傷害了我們的同胞對你的信任。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  許多志士險些因你的出賣而落入敵人的囹圄，無數戰士可能因你的背叛而無緣見到勝利的榮光。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你必須為你的行為付出代價。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他們......真的是因為我做的事而死的嗎？", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  昨天晚上，聚在那邊屋子裡的人，他們中的很大一部分是真心想迎接你，他們相信你可以給我們帶來好的變化！", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而現在，他們和這條街一樣被炸成了焦土。放這把火的人，難道是我？", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  閉嘴，叛徒！", "name": "深池士兵"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你這軟弱的投敵者，如何能理解烈士的決心？與其落入敵手，遭受羞辱和折磨，他們寧願昂首迎接領袖的火！", "name": "深池士兵"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他們是為了塔拉人的福祉，不得不在戰火中犧牲！", "name": "深池士兵"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  宣判吧，領袖，判她死刑！", "name": "深池士兵"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......死刑？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當然。你沒看見嗎？只有叛徒的死才能平息戰士們的怒火。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  另外——你看看周圍的當地人。他們想走近，又不敢。他們在恐懼我們，恐懼你。這正是讓他們徹底臣服的好機會。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  等你處死這個叛徒，他們就能學會，沒人能在背叛深池之後活下來。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒人能......背叛？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  西爾莎·凱利，你有想過背叛的後果嗎？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我......也許，我會死。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但我不後悔。既然你會因為我想救我的家人朋友而殺了我，那只能說明我做得對——要是沒人阻止的話，還會有更多人因你而死。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......你很有勇氣。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我沒聽錯吧，你誇一個叛徒有勇氣？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她也是我們的同胞。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  從她選擇擋路開始，她就不再是了。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我說，囉嗦這些有意義嗎？如果是她，根本就不會問這麼多。一個註定要死的人說的話，不應該對你產生影響。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是姐姐的話......她會怎麼做？"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都在這麼問。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......我不喜歡這麼想。我從來都，不喜歡。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  快點動手！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那麼多雙眼睛盯著呢。你拖得越久，就越顯得我們懦弱。誰願意跟隨一個懦弱的領袖？人民又怎麼會追隨一支懦弱的隊伍？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒給我選擇。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個孩子，不是我殺死的第一個同胞。那時候我才幾歲？她讓我燒死那個不願意賣麵包給我們的維多利亞商人。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忘了我是怎麼做的。我閉上眼舉起了小刀，可只是扎進了一堆焦臭的灰燼裡。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，灰越來越多。和這個孩子一樣，越有勇氣的人，他們燒得越快。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......西爾莎·凱利。我以深池領袖的名義，判處你死刑。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我會在這裡親手處決你。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  看來......我還是要死了。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......領袖。你是領袖，可能沒人能阻止你，我的家人們都還是會死。但你能不能告訴我，我們會勝利嗎？", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  會有那麼一天，我們塔拉人都能過上更好的生活？", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  會的。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好，那就好，至少在這一刻，我願意......相信。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你還有什麼話要說嗎？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  火......我看到了你槍尖的火。被燒死的時候會不會很痛？", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不，還是別告訴我，我不敢聽。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  求你，告訴我的爸爸媽媽，如果事情結束之後他們還能活著的話......", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我瞞著他們，在床頭第三個櫃子裡藏了一些錢，我想在下個月媽媽生日的時候給她買一束花......", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  告訴他們，我對不起大家。", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我答應你。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_213", "name2": "avg_npc_231", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗚......我不想死。我好害怕......", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊......哈......不知道明年春天，在燒焦了的土地上，柳樹還會不會發芽......", "name": "西爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_213"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ——", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  為了......深池！", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這句話......我說了無數次。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每說一次，我的胸腹都在灼痛中翻攪，就彷彿槍不在我的手上，而是正扎在我的體內。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一遍遍地告訴自己，生命易燃，他們都是燃料。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我也不例外。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#6"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......哈，死了。這還差不多。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#6"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  傳令下去，讓其他人都知道，叛徒已被處決。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#6"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  再有人想告密，就等著跟她一樣碎成炭渣吧。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#6"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是，長官。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  至於你，你今天到底怎麼回事？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼磨蹭，戰士們看到了，還以為他們的領袖會對叛徒心軟。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  喂，你該不會真心軟了吧？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#4"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這就是一個人，你昨天那一把火可是乾脆地燒掉了大半條街！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#6"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我還以為你終於像點樣子了呢，“領袖”。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我像樣子嗎？"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像什麼樣子？我很久沒注意到自己是什麼樣子了。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從小時候開始，我眼裡就只有她的樣貌，她的語氣，她的火。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她要我也變成這樣。我做不到，所以我註定只能藏在她的火光之下。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她又在發呆了。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  每次看到她擺出這副表情，我就想衝她的臉尖叫。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嫉妒了？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  少來刺我。我就是看不順眼她頂著這張臉，腦子裡卻全是廢水做的肥皂泡。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  為什麼領袖要把她擺在這個位置上？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  要不是那張天生的面孔，她不過是個廢物，連處決一個叛徒都做不好。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以你代她做了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她自己都搞不清楚，但我看得挺明白，她的火燒到之前，那女孩就已經被看不見的石錐刺穿了胸膛。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我實在忍不住！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  都是因為這個無恥的叛徒，我好不容易召集來這麼多有錢有勢的支持者，結果死的死，散的散。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哦？沒想到你還有一點憐憫之心。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈......就算是一群肉獸，也該發揮點作用再去死吧？現在倒好，砰一下，全都成了焦炭。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這麼乾脆地死了說不定是好事。別忘了，你那點貪心的小計畫，可差一點把我們都坑了進去。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我......我是為了領袖和深池！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  難道你不覺得她不配？哪怕她沒有帶人過來，我也能把小丘郡管好。不，是更好。我能做得更好。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  要是領袖能更信任我一些......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不配？你說的倒是沒錯。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  人啊，最好還是能看清楚些，別整天想著爬到不屬於自己的位置，否則的話，一個不小心就會跌下來，啪，粉身碎骨。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你是不是在罵我？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  怎麼會呢？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  走吧，別瞪著她生悶氣了。我們還要商量下一步該怎麼做。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “強盜”、“縱火者”、“會計”、“毒藥學者”、“囚犯”，還有“雄辯家”。昨天晚上發出的通知，算算時間，他們都該到了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  現在市政廳是我們的了，要員和貴族我們也控制了不少。但還不夠。我們得在領袖到這裡之前，把小丘郡徹底佔領。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......嘖。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  再咬的話，你的指甲就該禿了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#6"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  要你管。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  到時候別哭著求我再幫你塗個新的花樣。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我什麼時候在你面前哭過？！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......我就是不想把功勞拱手讓人。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  好啦好啦，我還不知道你？你是最早跟隨領袖的人之一，眼光也該放長遠些。不過一個小丘郡，就讓你心癢成這樣，你也不嫌丟人。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你是說......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#4"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  等這裡的事辦完，領袖需要有人替她跑一趟倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你不早說！快，趕緊走，我要在半天之內拿下小丘郡！", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們每個人心裡都有自己的欲望，光怪陸離，就連最烈的火都沒法一把燒得見底。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我的呢？我只想，躲起來......"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，影子能有逃開的權利嗎？"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  領袖。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_244", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  阿赫茉妮女士請您去開會。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_244", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我......一定要去嗎？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_244", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  呃，女士確實說了，要是您實在不想去，他們也會尊重您的意願。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231", "name2": "avg_npc_244", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  尊重......？她說得真好。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  士兵，你去告訴他們，一切按計畫進行。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他們知道自己的職責，不需要我來敦促。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  至於我，我需要安靜地思考。命令你的人好好守著，不要讓人來打擾我。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_244"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是，領袖。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_231"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我需要......一點時間......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這是......什麼東西？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_231"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在廢墟裡撿到了一張紙。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紙張十分脆弱，四角都已焦黑，一拿起來，半邊就化成了灰，紙上的文字也只可悲地剩下了一半。"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我何須灰心”"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“雖然大火燃盡了整片大地”"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“可我看到一個人的靈魂，在磅秤的另一端”"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是一首詩，一首缺失開頭的詩。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些字句看起來是剛剛寫就，墨水還沒有自然凝固，就已被火焚乾。"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我的火。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的靈魂......"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}